{"tid":1083199,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony 關閉北京廠房   Xperia 手機改往泰國生產","createTime":"2019-03-29T12:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T23:50:58.000Z","uid":73092,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c48c4d540c98e0342ef7b9e2c1b0e77e83644cb1","tid":1083199,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"路透社昨日引述 Sony 發言人指，集團將會在未來幾天關閉位於北京的智能手機廠房，並且將生產 Xperia 手機的基地遷移到泰國。報導指 Sony 將手機生產由中國大陸搬到泰國，是為了達到智能手機業務在 2020 年轉虧為盈的目標。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-03/29/212626/uniqlo_1_49681404819ef3b5bf3ae053face03ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-03%2F29%2F212626%2Funiqlo_1_49681404819ef3b5bf3ae053face03ad.jpg&h=4528b833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSony 發言人表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">將手機生產線由中國大陸搬到泰國，預計成本可以減少達 50%</span>。Sony 近年的業績強勁，但手機業務則有點滯後；不過近期傳出改革手機部門的消息，包括更換管理層、將手機合併到相機影音部門、修改出機策略和引進相機部門的技術等。Sony 亦嘗試改變手機的定價策略，並透過削減生產成本以提升利潤。"},{"pid":"f96d95a065b0564262596cdfd463dd0dca664233","tid":1083199,"uid":112583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:57:13.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778b26a9575516c806266bbfc8c3a32e7575c362","tid":1083199,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T21:59:22.000Z","msg":"秦國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ffc77bff6c9b4717d210a998790a322a5eeca1","tid":1083199,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T22:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sony手機都唔賣得，搬去邊都一樣"},{"pid":"38ef79dc29dcd982699e573adae8b727756b0658","tid":1083199,"uid":41545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"98ffc77bff